574
01:05:37,334 --> 01:05:40,599
l swear l had nothing to do with it.

575
01:05:40,770 --> 01:05:44,830
Why do you expect me
to listen to these lies?

576
01:05:45,007 --> 01:05:47,532
- Goodbye, Ernesto.
- No, no, no!

577
01:05:47,976 --> 01:05:50,705
Don't hang up.
We must have a meeting.

578
01:05:50,878 --> 01:05:53,813
- When?
- As soon as possible.

579
