665
01:16:36,728 --> 01:16:39,219
- Did this just happen?
- Just now.

666
01:16:42,866 --> 01:16:47,200
Send me all the stuff,
and we'll put a tail on him if we spot him.

667
01:16:47,703 --> 01:16:50,501
lf he's still alive. l've got to go.

668
01:16:55,110 --> 01:16:58,602
- A surgical strike, you said.
