671
01:17:06,953 --> 01:17:09,217
l'm not changing my mind.

672
01:17:09,856 --> 01:17:13,689
l hadn't counted on
this kind of collateral damage.

673
01:17:15,128 --> 01:17:18,153
- Neither had he.
- lt will be interpreted as l said.

674
01:17:18,329 --> 01:17:22,061
Rivalry that ended
in the blast of a car bomb.

675
01:17:22,234 --> 01:17:23,564
Goodnight.

676
01:17:38,881 --> 01:17:43,112
- Morning, Rose. Finish the report?
- Hot off the press.

677
01:17:45,986 --> 01:17:50,013
Could any of the bombing victims'
names be aliases?

678
01:17:50,490 --> 01:17:55,051
No. All lDs have been confirmed.
