695
01:19:27,973 --> 01:19:32,740
But nobody uses it.
Nobody can afford it except the military.

696
01:19:32,911 --> 01:19:38,177
An aerial bomb would do that.
But that's not an aerial bomb.

697
01:19:38,349 --> 01:19:39,680
- lt's not?
- No.

698
01:19:39,850 --> 01:19:43,478
