Here and here.

700
01:19:47,023 --> 01:19:50,685
- But there isn't.
- No bomb fragments.

701
01:20:34,529 --> 01:20:38,966
''Cellulose encased laser-guided bomb''...

702
01:20:41,102 --> 01:20:42,627
Paper.

703
