01:21:19,602 --> 01:21:23,799
We have something in common.
Neither of us can implement policy

705
01:21:23,972 --> 01:21:28,033
without at least tacit authorisation
from our employer.

706
01:21:28,209 --> 01:21:33,076
We also both know there are
American troops in Colombia

707
01:21:33,246 --> 01:21:35,840
fighting an illegal war.

708
01:21:37,316 --> 01:21:42,447
l will be at Hotel paloma de Oro
in panama City on Wednesday.

709
01:21:42,622 --> 01:21:44,248
l suggest we meet.

710
01:22:36,567 --> 01:22:40,628
- Six, this is point. Over.
- Six here.

711
01:22:41,972 --> 01:22:49,467
The stuff's here, a lot of it.
l'm also looking at 100-1 50 men, armed,

712
01:22:49,645 --> 01:22:52,442
waiting around for something. Over.

713
01:22:52,614 --> 01:22:55,139
Colombian Army? Over.

714
01:22:58,719 --> 01:23:02,119
Negative. They look like mercenaries.

715
